      | name     | password | token      | id |
      | Catrobat | 12345    | cccccccccc | 1  |
      | User1    | vwxyz    | aaaaaaaaaa | 2  |
    And there are projects:
      | id | name      | description | owned by | downloads | views | upload time      | version | file_size |
      | 1  | project 1 | p1          | Catrobat | 3         | 12    | 01.01.2013 12:00 | 0.8.5   | 1024      |
      | 2  | project 2 |             | Catrobat | 333       | 9     | 22.04.2014 13:00 | 0.8.5   | 2621440   |
      | 3  | project 3 |             | User1    | 133       | 33    | 01.01.2012 13:00 | 0.8.5   | 1337      |
    And the current time is "01.08.2014 13:00"

